body.description: Centrum Silver Multivitamin for Adults 50 Plus brings you a tailored senior multivitamin/multimineral supplement to help support full body wellness (1). This multivitamin contains Vitamin D and calcium to help support strong bones, B-Vitamins to help promote heart health, zinc to help support normal brain function, and lutein and Vitamins A, C, and E to help support healthy eyes (1, 2). Key nutrients in these multivitamins help fill in nutritional gaps to promote overall wellness and vitality (1). This multivitamin is verified Non-GMO (3) and gluten free for a variety of dietary preferences. These tablets feature a smooth coating that makes these adult vitamins easy to swallow. Simply take one of these vitamin supplements daily to provide your body with vitamins and minerals. Centrum Silver is the number 1 Doctor recommended multivitamin brand now shown to support memory and cognition in older adults (1). (1) These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease. (2) Not a replacement for cholesterol-lowering drugs (1) (3) Read more about our Non-GMO standard on Centrum's official website
